# ─── Root-level working files (brand originals, logos, blog drafts, etc.) ───
# Only /docs is deployed to GitHub Pages. Everything else at the project root
# (logos, photo originals, blog/, feed.xml, the saved live-site backup, .OLD files)
# stays local — not tracked, not deployed. The 5 photos USED by the site live inside
# docs/assets/img/ and ARE tracked.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/PRE-LAUNCH-CHECKLIST.md
!/docs/
